><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 15, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104bhn1665702735843.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bhn1665702735843.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bhn1665702735843.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"bhn1665702735843\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">MySQL \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"bhn1665702735843__mysql_159746\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The MySQL DBMS connector enables you to integrate MySQL databases with Uniface.\n </p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"bhn1665702735843__table_d4961e1_d4962e1_d4963e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bhn1665702735843__table_d4961e1_d4962e1_d4963e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Connector Feature</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bhn1665702735843__table_d4961e1_d4962e1_d4963e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bhn1665702735843__table_d4961e1_d4962e1_d4963e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Mnemonic</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bhn1665702735843__table_d4961e1_d4962e1_d4963e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">MQL</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bhn1665702735843__table_d4961e1_d4962e1_d4963e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Supported version</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bhn1665702735843__table_d4961e1_d4962e1_d4963e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">For the supported platforms and product versions, see the <a class=\"xref\" href=\"https://community.rocketsoftware.com/rocket-uniface-product-updates-108/uniface-product-availability-information-18191\" rel=\"external noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Platform Availability Matrix</a>.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bhn1665702735843__table_d4961e1_d4962e1_d4963e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Supported utilities</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bhn1665702735843__table_d4961e1_d4962e1_d4963e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Create Table and Load Definitions are supported. Create Scripts is not\n                        supported.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bhn1665702735843__table_d4961e1_d4962e1_d4963e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">SQL support</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bhn1665702735843__table_d4961e1_d4962e1_d4963e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Supported.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bhn1665702735843__table_d4961e1_d4962e1_d4963e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Stored procedures support</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bhn1665702735843__table_d4961e1_d4962e1_d4963e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Supported.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bhn1665702735843__p_d53372e1_d53373e1_d53374e1\">To use the Uniface MQL U5.0 connector, you need to copy <span class=\"ph filepath\">libmysql.dll</span> from connector folder of the MySQL installation to the <span class=\"ph filepath\">common/bin</span> folder of the Uniface installation.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"bhn1665702735843__note_w630ab1b5b7_w631ab1b5_w632ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> Be sure to copy the correct version. The 32-bit and 64-bit versions are not binary compatible.</div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jtn1665702949730.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Support for Unicode in the MQL Connector</a><p>The Uniface MQL connector can support Unicode. By default, Unicode support is disabled.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bth1665702949940.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Environment Considerations for MySQL</a></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ikq1665702951085.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Database Access on MySQL</a><p>The MQL connector uses the MySQL client library to connect to the server and manipulate the DBMS.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xmi1665702939210.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>RecordManagement</a></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/knl1665702951724.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Naming Rules on MySQL</a></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jtc1665702704700.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Referential Integrity Management on MySQL</a><p>Referential integrity is handled by Uniface.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/enx1665702664511.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Data Retrieval on MySQL</a><p>The offset option, order by, and where clauses of the read ProcScript statement are supported, with some restrictions.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yhg1665702777428.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>SQL Support on MySQL</a><p>Both the sql ProcScript command and SQL Editor are supported.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jep1665702777506.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>MySQL Service Stored Procedures</a><p>Service stored procedures are supported for the MySQL connector.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qwi1665702727550.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>MySQL Data Packing</a></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uuw1665702730668.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>MySQL Connector Options</a><p>You can assign connector options by setting USYS$MQL_PARAMS in the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526056\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526056\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "MySQL Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 15, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 MySQL The MySQL DBMS connector enables you to integrate MySQL databases with Uniface. Connector Feature Description Mnemonic MQL Supported version For the supported platforms and product versions, see the Platform Availability Matrix . Supported utilities Create Table and Load Definitions are supported. Create Scripts is not supported. SQL support Supported. Stored procedures support Supported. To use the Uniface MQL U5.0 connector, you need to copy libmysql.dll from connector folder of the MySQL installation to the common/bin folder of the Uniface installation. Note: Be sure to copy the correct version. The 32-bit and 64-bit versions are not binary compatible. Related Links Support for Unicode in the MQL Connector The Uniface MQL connector can support Unicode. By default, Unicode support is disabled. Environment Considerations for MySQL Database Access on MySQL The MQL connector uses the MySQL client library to connect to the server and manipulate the DBMS. RecordManagement Naming Rules on MySQL Referential Integrity Management on MySQL Referential integrity is handled by Uniface. Data Retrieval on MySQL The offset option, order by, and where clauses of the read ProcScript statement are supported, with some restrictions. SQL Support on MySQL Both the sql ProcScript command and SQL Editor are supported. MySQL Service Stored Procedures Service stored procedures are supported for the MySQL connector. MySQL Data Packing MySQL Connector Options You can assign connector options by setting USYS$MQL_PARAMS in the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}